<html><head><meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark"><meta charset="utf-8"></head><body><pre>{"id":381,"date":"2015-08-24T11:20:29","date_gmt":"2015-08-24T01:20:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/melbacg.wordpress.com\/?p=381"},"modified":"2015-08-24T11:20:29","modified_gmt":"2015-08-24T01:20:29","slug":"29-aug-stop-the-bigots-in-bendigo-no-to-fascism-no-to-islamophobia","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/29-aug-stop-the-bigots-in-bendigo-no-to-fascism-no-to-islamophobia\/","title":{"rendered":"29 AUG Stop the bigots in Bendigo! No to fascism, no to Islamophobia"},"content":{"rendered":"&lt;p&gt;Fascist group the \u2018United Patriots Front\u2019 (UPF) are planning to descend on Bendigo on Saturday, 29 August outside the Town Hall in order to protest the construction of a mosque.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The mosque was the subject of an unsuccessful legal challenge a few weeks ago (see : http:\/\/www.theage.com.au\/victoria\/bendigo-mosque-survives-legal-challenge-gets-green-light-for-planning-permit-20150806-gisq9z.html, Rania Spooner, The Age, August 6, 2015) but may be subject to further challenge in the courts.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The Campaign Against Racism and Fascism is mobilising against the UPF and to defend the right of Muslims, in Bendigo and elsewhere, to have their own house of worship.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;CARF will be assembling on &lt;strong&gt;Saturday 29 August&lt;\/strong&gt; at &lt;strong&gt;1:00 p.m.&lt;\/strong&gt; at:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bendigo Trades Hall&lt;br \/&gt;\n40 View St&lt;br \/&gt;\nBendigo 3550&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We will march to the Town Hall at 1:30.  For more information, see the Facebook event:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/events\/740339059424914\/&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;For those travelling from Melbourne, the MACG advises taking reasonable care when travelling to and from Bendigo.  If you travel by train, don&amp;#8217;t be conspicuous.  If you travel by car, park it in a side street and not at the railway station.  And take a map or two so you don&amp;#8217;t get lost.&lt;\/p&gt;\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Fascist group the \u2018United Patriots Front\u2019 (UPF) are planning to descend on Bendigo on Saturday, 29 August outside the Town Hall in order \n&lt;a class=\"moretag\" href=\"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/29-aug-stop-the-bigots-in-bendigo-no-to-fascism-no-to-islamophobia\/\"&gt; [...]&lt;\/a&gt;","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1867,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-381","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/381","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=381"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/381\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1867"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=381"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=381"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/melbacg.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=381"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}</pre><div class="json-formatter-contai